sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Staff as Staff Discord
    participant DC as Discord
    participant CMD as Command<br/>Handler
    participant BE as Backend<br/>Express API
    participant DB as Database<br/>PostgreSQL
    participant Discord as Discord<br/>Service

    Note over Staff, Discord: Command !status - Update Status Tiket

    Staff ->> DC: !status #12 investigasi<br/>Ada anomali jaringan
    activate DC
    DC ->> CMD: messageCreate event
    deactivate DC
    activate CMD
    CMD ->> CMD: Parse - ticketId=12,<br/>action=investigasi, note=...

    CMD ->> DB: ticket.findById (12)
    activate DB
    DB -->> CMD: ticket (type=INCIDENT, status=OPEN)
    deactivate DB

    alt Tiket tidak ditemukan
        CMD -->> DC: reply - Ticket tidak ditemukan
    else Type INCIDENT - action valid
        CMD ->> DB: ticket.update (INVESTIGASI, note)
        activate DB
        DB -->> CMD: updated ticket
        deactivate DB
        CMD ->> DB: activity.create (STATUS_UPDATED)
        CMD ->> Discord: updateThreadTitle (ticket)
        activate Discord
        Discord -->> CMD: updated
        deactivate Discord
        CMD ->> Discord: updateTicketMessage (ticket)
        activate Discord
        Discord -->> CMD: updated
        deactivate Discord
        CMD ->> BE: triggerWorkflow (status.changed)
        activate BE
        BE -->> CMD: triggered
        deactivate BE
        CMD -->> DC: reply sukses - Status INVESTIGASI
        activate DC
        DC -->> Staff: Konfirmasi status terupdate
        deactivate DC
    end
    deactivate CMD

    Note over Staff, Discord: Command !assign - Assign Petugas

    Staff ->> DC: !assign #12 Budi, Siti, Tim Jaringan
    activate DC
    DC ->> CMD: messageCreate event
    deactivate DC
    activate CMD
    CMD ->> CMD: Parse assignees list
    CMD ->> DB: ticket.update (assignee list)
    activate DB
    DB -->> CMD: updated
    deactivate DB
    CMD ->> DB: activity.create (ASSIGNED)
    CMD ->> Discord: updateTicketMessage (ticket)
    activate Discord
    Discord -->> CMD: updated
    deactivate Discord
    CMD -->> DC: reply konfirmasi assignee
    activate DC
    DC -->> Staff: Petugas berhasil di-assign
    deactivate DC
    deactivate CMD

    Note over Staff, Discord: Command !evidence - Upload Attachment

    Staff ->> DC: !evidence + attach file screenshot
    activate DC
    DC ->> CMD: messageCreate + attachment
    deactivate DC
    activate CMD
    CMD ->> CMD: Ambil attachment URL
    CMD ->> DB: ticket.update (evidence_attachment append)
    activate DB
    DB -->> CMD: updated
    deactivate DB
    CMD ->> DB: activity.create (evidence)
    CMD -->> DC: reply - Evidence tersimpan
    activate DC
    DC -->> Staff: Evidence berhasil dilampirkan
    deactivate DC
    deactivate CMD